0 kr\nAfter 00.00: 40 kr\n\n-----------------------\nFACEBOOK GROUP:\n----------------\nhttp://www.facebook.com/groups/bachatanights/ \n\n\n\n----\n\nSPECIAL WORKSHOPS IN KIZOMBA & SEMBA - KIZOMBA IN SWEDEN 1 YEAR CELEBRATION:\n\nJoao N Rocha and Kizombafeber sends this message: \nhttp://www.facebook.com/events/429467170440347/\n\nHello dear Kizombies!\n\nThis 10th of November we will have many reasons to celebrate! Makes 1 year that kizomba came to Stockholm and it's also a very important date, the 11th of November Angola celebrates it's Independence day! So therefore we organise something special for you to not only Celebrate the day of this amazing country where kizomba comes from as to pay a tribute to Jenni Kasajima who took the 1st initiative to make a kizomba event in Stockholm! \n\nWe have among us a very good teacher visiting Stockholm, Ruddy, from Paris! He already is a known face among some of the Stockholm Kizombies so this time we will have the opportunity to have a 3h Workshop with him!\n\nSaturday the 10th November:\nfrom 1pm till 2pm Kizomba improver/intermediate\nfrom 2pm till 3pm Kizomba intermediate/Advance\nfrom 3pm till 4pm Semba Improvers\n\nLocation will be at Salsa Akademien!\n\nWe have a special deal with Salsa Akademien, for those who participate at the workshops you will have 50% discount either the Party entrance or the drop ins which include party.\n\nPrices:\n\nSingle registration 450kr in advance\nCouple registration 350kr in advance\nat the door will be 100kr more!\n\nTo register send and email with your name and email address to reservations@kizombafeber.se informing you're registering for the 1 year Kizomba in Stockholm!\nhttp://www.facebook.com/events/429467170440347/", :start_time => "2012-11-10 13:30:00", :end_time => "2012-11-10 19:00:00", :address => "Odengatan 87, 113 22 Stockholm, Sweden", :fb_id => 360600960697146, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc6/2767