  { :name => "Mardi HEChange - ZAZ Bar", :longitude => -73.57961159999999, :latitude => 45.52265999999999, :gmaps => true, :description => "*English follows*\nLa relâche est finie. Il est grand tant de se retrouver autour d'une bière et d'un billard. Venez partager vos histoires de Cuba, Cancun ou New York avant de vous déchainer sur la piste de danse! \n\nComme toujours des spéciaux sur l'alcool très avantageux :\n- 9$ le pichet\n- 4,25$ le drink\n\nDe quoi bien s'échauffer pour la Queue Leu Leu ce Samedi (https://www.facebook.com/events/443026735745040/?fref=ts) !\n\n::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: ENGLISH ::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::\n\nFall break is now over. It's time to share our stories of Cuba, Cancun or NYC around a fresh beer and pool before dancing all night long!\n\nAs always, enjoy great prices :\n- 9$ for a pitcher\n- 4,25$ for a drink\n\nSomething to warm you up before la Queue Leu Leu on Saturday (https://www.facebook.com/events/443026735745040/?fref=ts) !\n\nYour VP Party,\nPierre", :start_time => "2012-11-06 22:30:00", :end_time => "2012-11-07 01:30:00", :address => "4301 Rue St Denis, Montreal, QC H2J 2K8, Canada", :fb_id => 495180867181727, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc6/276431_495180867181727_1174500999_q.jpg", :atenders => 30, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-11-05 22:10:28", :updated_at => "2012-11-05 22:10:28" },
