  { :name => "Catholic Gators- SEEK2013!", :longitude => -81.5594744, :latitude => 28.3663438, :gmaps => true, :description => "Join us as we bring 300 Catholic Gators to Orlando, FL for SEEK2013! Jan 2-6 in Orlando, FL!\n\nFOCUS National Conference is BACK and with a new branding: SEEK2013. It will be hosted at the luxurious Swan & Dolphin Resort right here in Orlando, FL!! Jan 2nd-6th. You do NOT want to miss out on this. Join us as we bring 300 Catholic Gators to this event of a lifetime!\n\nWhat is SEEK2013?\n\nSEEK is a gathering of college students on a journey. It’s a place where we can come together to take on some of life’s BIGGER questions and, like guides along the way, learn from one another where wisdom and experience lead. Life is meant to be lived and in order to live it to the fullest, we need to heed the wisdom that calls us to ‘ask, seek and knock’ to discover who we are, where we’re going and what motivates us.\n\nPresented by FOCUS, the Fellowship of Catholic University Students, SEEK 2013 is an adventurous five-day event in Orlando from January 2nd – 6th. With unexpected twists and turns, you will be challenged, inspired and left wanting more.\n\nDon’t go it alone, let’s seek together.", :start_time => "2013-01-02 02:00:00", :end_time => "2013-01-03 02:00:00", :address => "Walt Disney World Dolphin, Orlando, FL 32836, USA", :fb_id => 418423574883187, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc7/373337_418423574883187_771094828_q.jpg", :atenders => 60, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-11-05 22:14:42", :updated_at => "2012-11-05 22:14:42" },
