  { :name => "Absolutely FREE Gator Salsa FALL EXTRAVAGANZA with Salomon Amaya of Houston!!!", :longitude => -82.333203, :latitude => 29.65137, :gmaps => true, :description => "Gator Salsa Club proudly presents its FALL SOCIAL EXTRAVAGANZA!!\n\nWith a high attendance of over 300 PEOPLE at our semester socials, this time we're doing it even bigger and better than ever with TOTALLY FREE workshops and social dancing! This year we have the amazing Salomon Amaya coming all the way from Houston! Make sure to save the date because you won't want to miss out! \nDance the night away with the best Salsa, Bachata, and Cha Cha music spun by the one and only DJ Josbell! \n\n--------------------\nFREE DAYTIME WORKSHOPS - 2pm to 6pm\nFREE SOCIAL DANCING AND PERFORMANCES -10pm to 3am\n--------------------\n\nGator Salsa Fall Extravaganza Workshop Schedule!!!\n \n2-3pm\nCorazon Dancers (Tallahassee) - LA Salsa and Shines\nAzucar Dance Company (Tallahassee) - Casino Salsa Styling\nSalsa Caliente (Gainesville) - New York Salsa Ladies Styling\n \n3-4pm\nGator Salsa - Advanced Casino Salsa\nGator Salsa - Advanced New York Salsa\n \n4-5pm\nLatin Dance Club (Tampa) - Advanced Bachata\nSalomon Amaya (Houston) - LA Salsa Musicality\n \n5-6pm:\nOmar Clinton (Gainesville) – Cha-Cha!\nSalomon Amaya (Houston) - LA Salsa Turn Patterns\n\n--------------------\n\nSTICK AROUND PERFORMANCE ANNOUNCEMENT COMING SOON!!!!\n\n--------------------\n\nIf you have any questions about this event, feel free to post on the event wall! :)", :start_time => "2012-11-17 14:00:00", :end_time => "2012-11-18 03:30:00", :address => "20 SW 8th St, Gainesville, FL 32601, USA", :fb_id => 253030754819796, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-ash4/188045_253030754819796_2044530723_q.jpg", :atenders => 155, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-11-05 22:18:59", :updated_at => "2012-11-05 22:18:59" },
  { :name => "EUCSA-EKSS SINGLE PARTY 11/11/12", :longitude => -3.1888369, :latitude => 55.95118549999999, :gmaps => true, :description => "Dear All, \n\nWe are inviting you to the one and only EUCSA-EKSS Single Party of the year! If you are still single, still longing for love, but have not yet succeed it in finding the right person, then this party is RIGHT for you! This is a FABULOUS opportunity for YOU to find your LOVE. Don’t leave it to the FATE, it’s YOUR choice to make it happen. So COME and JOIN the party, you will not regret it! \n\nTICKET SALE: MON-SUN 12-2pm IN FRONT OF THE MAIN LIBRARY\n£10 for members of EUCSA/EKSS (please bring membership card) \n£12 for non-members\n£15 at door\n\nLADIES GET FREE ENTRY BEFORE 10PM!!\n\nVIP-Package: \n\nDIAMOND VIP (£300) :  8 VIP tickets, one bottle of drink (JD, vodka), and roses \n\nPLATINIUM VIP (£260) : 6 VIP tickets, one bottle of drink ( JD, vodka) \n\nGOLD VIP (£120) : 6 VIP tickets and roses \n\nQUEUE JUMPING EXCLUSIVE TO VIP!!\n\nFor more info about the Vip-package or ticket sell, please contact:\nZhengqi Song: 07545325198 \nor Zehong Li: 07714202008.\n\nThere are also loads of events lined up, include 'beauty' auction, 'party queen' competition, and much more. COME AND FIND OUT MORE! \n\nREMEMBER: Bring your ID for the club entry! \n\nHope to see you all there!\n\nLove, \nEUCSA –EKSS team xxxxx\n", :start_time => "2012-11-11 16:00:00", :end_time => "2012-11-11 19:00:00", :address => "1-3 Market St, Old Town, Edinburgh, Midlothian EH1 1DE, UK", :fb_id => 132671603547760, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-ash4/373174_132671603547760_1983995684_q.jpg", :atenders => 41, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-11-05 22:19:01", :updated_at => "2012-11-05 22:19:01" },
  { :name => "Medic Frat Party", :longitude => -3.1878263, :latitude => 55.94596749999999, :gmaps => true, :description => "Beer pong, Kegs, Red cups.\n\nFor one night and one night only.\nAMERICA IS COMING TO TOWN.\n\nYou know the score by now... \n- £5/£6 (members/non-members)\n- ALL INCLUSIVE BOOZE ALL NIGHT\n- ALL-AMERICAN ENTERTAINMENT\n     - Kegs and the mandatory kegstands. Get practicing.\n     - American themed decoration\n     - Red cups\n     - Body shots on the bar\n\nAnd of course let's not forget the FRAT GAMES:\n-Beer Pong\n-Flip Cup\n-Landmines\n-Boat Race\n\nAnd after the success of the last social:\n-Spin the Bottle (things escalated rather quickly)\n-Never Have I Ever\n-Truth or Dare (the RMS witnessed the first ever Back Sack and Crack last week from this game. For those who don't know what this is, you are by far a better human being)\n\nAs if that isn't enough to make you clear your diaries for the 6th of Novermber, here are the details:\n\nWhat you need to know:\n\nDate: Tuesday 6th November\nTime: 20:00\nLocation: RhoMuSigma Frat House (The RMS)\n\nWho is welcome: Absolutely everybody, everybody, everybodaaay... And your grandpa. He's not seen the USA since the war and he's been feeling lonely with your Granny being out all these Tuesdays.\n\nHope you can all join us for what promises to be an interesting night!", :start_time => "2012-11-06 15:00:00", :end_time => "2012-11-06 22:00:00", :address => "5/1 Bristo Square, University of Edinburgh, Old Town, Edinburgh, City of Edinburgh EH8 9AL, UK", :fb_id => 451648081543426, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc7/373188_451648081543426_883276001_q.jpg", :atenders => 74, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-11-05 22:19:03", :updated_at => "2012-11-05 22:19:03" },
