  { :name => "Kendrick Lamar + Pusha T + Kid Ink performing LIVE @ BFF", :longitude => -80.239167, :latitude => 26.363779, :gmaps => true, :description => "***BLACK FRIDAY FESTIVAL***\n\nKendrick Lamar+ Pusha T + Kid Ink performing LIVE                                  \n@ SUNSET COVE AMPHITHEATER \nNovember 23rd, 2012 (Black Friday, day after Thanksgiving)\nHost: DJ IRIE (Official Miami Heat DJ)\n\nGET ONLINE TICKETS HERE: http://BFFtickets.com/\n**www.BFFtickets.com**\n**www.BFFtickets.com**\n**$30 TICKETS ON SALE NOW!\n\n**All ages are welcome**\n\nOfficial Trailer: http://youtu.be/OT_v18WvDSc\nOfficial Trailer: http://youtu.be/OT_v18WvDSc\n\nKendrick Lamar's fan page\nhttps://fb.com/KendrickLamarmusic\n\nPusha T's fan page\nhttps://www.facebook.com/PushaT?fref=ts\n\nKid Ink's fan page\nhttps://www.facebook.com/OfficialKidInk?ref=ts&fref=ts\n\nUSA Today article featuring Kendrick Lamar\n\nhttp://usatoday.com/story/life/music/2012/10/21/kendrick-lamar-on-the-verge-good-kid/1642515/\n\n*MORE ARTISTS TO BE ANNOUNCED!!\n\n\nBlack Friday Festival marks the first day of the official Holiday season! This year rising Hip-Hop sensation Kendrick Lamar is taking center stage with special host DJ Irie of the Miami Heat!\n\nA one of a kind Festival bringing you various blends of multiple music genres throughout the night. This Black Friday will have a strong influence on hiphop, but will include an array of music and performances by Makayla Duvall, EDM DJ Demetrius, Miami's own Electro/Hip Hop artist Emir Duru, & Pop/ Electro singer Ty Sade! Black Friday Festival provides a new age of music blend with some of the biggest rising stars.\n\nWe have entered into a new age of pop culture where music has progressed and boundaries have been torn down between different genres. This Festival brings to you the latest sounds of music and the hottest artists of the year! Most importantly please remember to come ready to experience \"The Best Deal in Live Music\" and give yourself a time to remember during the beginning of this Holiday season!\n\nThere will be food, beer, and alcohol available! Dont forget to purchase your limited edition BFF tshirt online or at the show! Valet parking is available.\n\nAll ages are welcome!\n\nFor tickets or more information contact:\n\nDarius Sanchez   407-252-3054\nCasey Cummings 561 305 2850", :start_time => "2012-11-23 18:00:00", :end_time => "2012-11-24 12:00:00", :address => "12245 Glades Rd, Boca Raton, FL 33498, USA", :fb_id => 197571607043983, :owner_id => nil, :city => nil, :country => nil, :picture => "http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc6/188128_197571607043983_1623371891_q.jpg", :atenders => 1637, :privacy => nil, :created_at => "2012-11-05 22:27:10", :updated_at => "2012-11-05 22:27:10" },
